<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.2">
<l>eṉṉeñci ṉāṉōkkik kāṇī reṉṉai muṉiyātē</l>
<l>teṉṉaṉ cōlait tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>miṉṉu nūluṅ kuṇṭalamu mārviṟ ṟirumaṟuvu</l>
<l>maṉṉum pūṇu nāṉkutōḷum vanteṅku niṉṟiṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See looking at [it] with my heart, without disapproving of me.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Southern Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with good groves,</l>
<l>the flashing thread, the earring, the spot [that is] Śrī on the chest,</l>
<l>the permanent ornament and the four arms come everywhere [and] stay put.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
